QuestData.Title: WANTED: Venombarb
QuestData.Description: Posted by: Hutou Featherwind$B$BVenombarb is feared in the skies above Arak, even by the high arakkoa.$B$BShe has made air travel difficult for our riders, preventing vital supplies from reaching Axefall.$B$BI require no proof of her demise, simply ensure her screech never again echoes among the spires.$B$BShe nests above the howling crag to the northeast.
QuestData.RewardText: A thousand thanks to you, commander. I will call for more supply runs immediately.
